name: Externat
description: Have u ever imagined youself as a school shooter? Nope? Now is the TIME! This is the map of a real school with the rooms, that have the exact look (on the certain time 2k17). So, take a role of a killer. Everything that u need - you already have. Guns and ammo. Maybe you will find more weapons in the school. Who knows... Don't forget about security that works at school. Rip him up and execute everyone, who you want. Only god is a judge for you now. And also a cops, that will be wainting you outside and will be doing everything to neutralize you.
